{"type": "article", "id": 15561, "title": "“男友力”破表的毛衣，你可得好好选", "description": "秋天，一个适合谈恋爱的季节。冬天，一个适合谈恋爱的季节。春天……", "date": "2015-09-25T16:19:53Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 2499, "name": "毛衣"}, {"id": 8289, "name": "针织"}, {"id": 16660, "name": "开衫"}, {"id": 16661, "name": "圆领"}, {"id": 16662, "name": "百搭"}, {"id": 9519, "name": "Thom Browne"}, {"id": 779, "name": "Prada"}, {"id": 671, "name": "Gucci"}, {"id": 1060, "name": "H&M"}, {"id": 248, "name": "COS"}], "category": 19, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 16, "praise_count": 167, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606071634455v8oL9HJUkyIRupa.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这世界上最适合男人的可能是西装，没错。但像毛衣这样居家旅行必备、舒适保暖、外穿内搭兼可、粗织的毛绒绒看起来很温柔、贴身针织又很有型的可刚（gong）可柔（shou）单品，实在是值得拥有。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071634360RNQSby7I8W4s9jH.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.68674699\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t另外，请忘了你脑海中“N 匹狼”牌、村支书身上的老头衫，那并不是世界的真相。（本来要放两张图用以示范失败的案例，但实在太碍眼还是直接进入下一环节吧）。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607163437xamJb3RHAtzTyYpn.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.59134615\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t所谓毛衣的范围其实有点广，既有面料上兔毛、羊毛、针织之分，还有各种款，高领、圆领、V 领……以及男士专属的前方有纽扣或拉链的开衫款毛衣。可以来看看<span style=\"text-align:left;\">秋季新款那些不错的毛衣单品。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:left;\"><span style=\"text-align:left;\">Gucci</span><span style=\"text-align:left;\"> 使用了很多自然中花鸟鱼虫的元素，比如下面两套</span><a href=\"http://www.gucci.com/ca-en/styles/410405Z581A4029#\" target=\"_blank\">彩虹和小鸟</a>、<a href=\"http://www.gucci.com/ca-en/styles/410405Z581A4029#\" target=\"_blank\">老虎</a><span style=\"text-align:left;\">图案。</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607163437rAmjeOJbITkL3Fap.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" style=\"text-align:center;\" data-ratio=\"0.52138728\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span style=\"text-align:left;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<a href=\"http://www.gucci.com/ca-en/styles/410405Z581A4029#\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607163438aNXS5G4fdws2eyok.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.54011976\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\tGucci 女装热衷的书呆子气质学院风，这里可以有简单的纯白 V 领粗织款，领口和下摆红黑条纹挺常见，内搭衬衫的优雅穿法你们也都会。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607163438BXiMIAStJ3whOTWP.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.52138728\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<a href=\"http://www.vogue.com/fashion-shows/spring-2016-menswear/prada/slideshow/collection#13\" target=\"_blank\">Prada 2016 年春季新款</a>也有童趣印花：\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607163439p7MQnVLd8RIurGeF.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.7537037\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<span><a href=\"http://www.ssense.com/en-us/men/product/comme-des-garcons-homme-plus/grey-black-asymmetric-sweater/1229543?utm_source=6157042&amp;utm_medium=affiliate&amp;utm_campaign=generic&amp;utm_term=10492063\" target=\"_blank\"></a><span><a href=\"http://www.ssense.com/en-us/men/product/comme-des-garcons-homme-plus/grey-black-asymmetric-sweater/1229543?utm_source=6157042&amp;utm_medium=affiliate&amp;utm_campaign=generic&amp;utm_term=10492063\" target=\"_blank\">COMME des GARÇONS 的不对称款</a>：</span></span> \r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607163439NEkWIj64Rts7vuVA.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.67037037\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\tOpening Ceremony 出了彩条<a href=\"http://openingceremony.us/products.asp?menuid=1&amp;designerid=6&amp;productid=146790&amp;sproductid=146792\" target=\"_blank\">柯达系列</a>和<a href=\"http://openingceremony.us/products.asp?menuid=1&amp;designerid=6&amp;productid=146790&amp;sproductid=146792\" target=\"_blank\">双层</a>的：\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607163440OjdbMwn4vcEXVNSD.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.60257681\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/2016060716344003fHsezr41DJTu5i.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75621891\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\tThom Browne 的开衫和毛衣，最经典是袖子上的三道横条纹。右边<a href=\"http://www.mrporter.com/en-gb/mens/thom_browne/slim-fit-whale-jacquard-wool-blend-sweater/593633\" target=\"_blank\">鲸鱼印花的新款</a>也有这个设计：\r\n\t<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607163440uKDnig4FMP7RV5SJ.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.53686934\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n\t</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\tAlexander Wang 的黑色高领，领子处特别的印花像是围了丝巾：\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607163441sT6WkJzNyIn7cpqx.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.71574074\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\tNeil Barrett 最经典的是那款领口一圈小闪电的毛衣，新一季走秀款的<a href=\"http://www.neilbarrett.com/it/collectionsMens.php\" target=\"_blank\">半拉链半袖印花</a>挺百搭：\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607163442M0Vvtbr64jIgeUqy.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.70925926\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\tGudrun &amp; Gudrun 的<a href=\"http://www.gudrungudrun.com/sweaters-for-men.aspx\" target=\"_blank\">几款粉嫩条纹毛衣</a>配色也不错，暖男气质骤升：\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607163442jRu8YHOZ4sIr2Nd5.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.72644928\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607163443BZXvJHVWRs8epqmc.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.45634459\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t要么在领口上做文章，像<a href=\"http://www.cosstores.com/us/Men/New/Wide-neck_wool_jumper/17956276-18281831.1#c-15133319\" target=\"_blank\"> Cos 这两款</a>，一字领和几何形状的开口：\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607163443qHIM6PknfLQVdoND.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.7537037\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\tJ.Crew 有<a href=\"http://www.jcrew.com/mens_category/sweaters/LAMBSWOOL/PRDOVR~E0788/E0788.jsp\" target=\"_blank\">两款靠颜色取胜</a>的，价格也不贵，美国官网上卖 70 美元：\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607163444M3PmL5k4tHeYi2T0.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.50185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<a href=\"http://www.hm.com/us/products/men/jumpers_cardigans\" target=\"_blank\">还有更便宜的 H&amp;M</a><span>，下图分别是 30 和 60 美元：</span> \r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607163444nUs5eEGAN67pW04f.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.59196891\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\tH&amp;M <a href=\"http://www.hm.com/us/product/31001?article=31001-A\" target=\"_blank\">不同的粗细纹路</a>：\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607163445WR6LBblPGXAOmvMf.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.58703704\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}